result.name: 嘉潤粥店

reviews.text: Not a bad place for decent Cantonese breakfast. Cheap, fresh and no msg. Will come back for more

Was told to try congee when in Hong Kong and stumbled upon this place on the way to the train station. 
The fried bread by the entrance lured me in. The waitress knew some English so I was able to get a table order. There was a menu on the wall but it was in Chinese, I was handed a menu with English on it. It didn't take long to get the congee. It was nice but think that the fried bread made it much better.
Really cheap breakfast which was fairly filling.
An old style Cantonese congee and fry noodle food shop.
Affordable and delicious
Freshly prepared food, open early for light sleeper.

reviews.text: 蒸飯好食，牙口不好的推薦，綠豆沙（有陳皮）味道香^_^

Splendida esperienza! Nonostante il problema linguistico siamo stati trattati come amici,ci hanno aperto i tegami per farci scegliere cosa mangiare, ci siamo fatti consigliare e abbiamo mangiato divinamente. 
Location tipica.prezzo veramente onestissimo. 
Ci torneremo sicuramente anche domani sera.
粥底已經唔好, 炒麵又唔掂, 買艇仔粥冇花生, 個後生女店員 Heh到發夢❗😠 食唔食呢間閣下自己選擇, 我就一定唔會再幫襯❗❗❗
好好吃 便宜，豆漿好喝
可以一試無妨
